{"tid":847221,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《八個女人一台戲 》預告釋出","createTime":"2018-10-04T04:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T16:31:12.000Z","uid":202557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec930f9654285c3bb10d3f8bd5638358fbf1de3","tid":847221,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/122450_68a2a838c57aa3e167e8b132be30ae86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F122450_68a2a838c57aa3e167e8b132be30ae86.png&h=9ed83587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關錦鵬執導<br />\n編劇：關錦鵬、魏紹恩<br />\n<br />\n 領銜主演 ：鄭秀文、梁詠琪<br />\n特別演出 ：白百何<br />\n主演：齊溪、周家怡、商天娥<br />\n 友情演出：趙雅芝、林保怡、甘國亮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本片以中環大會堂為主要背景，講述用盡心機、勾心鬥角、爾虞我詐、女人之間的鬥爭。袁秀靈（鄭秀文 飾）及何玉紋（梁詠琪 飾）二人同為話劇團成員，何玉紋因袁秀靈當年「搶走」《胭脂案》一角，一直懷恨在心，並退出舞台。多年後二人又再合作舞台劇《壹世人倆姊妹》，心結未解而且互不相讓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GoldenSceneHK/videos/302353520555917/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGoldenSceneHK%2Fvideos%2F302353520555917%2F&d=HOg1Gf%2FEMHIvan3hf%2B7tMsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=374c8112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GoldenSceneHK/videos/302353520555917/</a>"},{"pid":"7e8b8556e01021cc89fdbba4c5138a8c14637fb6","tid":847221,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"睇錯以為係長恨歌造型<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/122627_60b9be68f589c868635e06396350e893.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F122627_60b9be68f589c868635e06396350e893.png&h=751c63f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/122635_cffcf1dbd7de60e1c7fd41fbcc3305dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupl